tp://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/pretty-pinterest.jpg" alt="Pretty Pinterest WordPress Plugin" title="Pretty Pinterest WordPress Plugin" width="500" height="162" class="size-full wp-image-1649" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Pretty Pinterest WordPress Plugin</p></div></p>\n<h3><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/pinterest-pin-it-button/" title="Pinterest Pin it Button" target="_blank">Pinterest &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button</a></h3>\n<p>Add a Pinterest &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button to your site to let your visitors easily pin your awesome content!<br />\nTake advantage of the exploding traffic Pinterest is generating by encouraging your readers to pin your content using this simple &#8220;Pin It&#8221; button.<br />\n<div id="attachment_1650" class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 510px"><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/pinterest-pin-it-button/" title="Pinterest Pin it Button WordPress Plugin" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/pin-it-button.jpg" alt="Pinterest Pin it Button WordPress Plugin" title="Pinterest Pin it Button WordPress Plugin" width="500" height="162" class="size-full wp-image-1650" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Pinterest Pin it Button WordPress Plugin</p></div></p>\n<h2>Premium Pinterest WordPress Plugins</h2>\n<h3><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/pinterest-auto-pin-for-wordpress/1761839?ref=neel" title="Pinterest Auto Pin For WordPress" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Pinterest Auto Pin For WordPress</a></h3>\n<p>Pinterest Auto Pin for WordPress allows you to quickly and easily add hover – over pin it buttons to your images on the fly making them instantly pinable to any board on Pinterest!<br />\n<div id="attachment_1652" class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 510px"><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/pinterest-auto-pin-for-wordpress/1761839?ref=neel"><img src="http://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/autopin-pinterest.jpg" alt="autopin pinterest wo