To get post count of category having category id 5\n?&gt;\n</pre>\n<p>This code snippet is useful to get total post count from category and its child categories.<br />\nChange 5 with your category id for which you want total post count.</p>\n<h3>Reference</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/support/topic/how-to-display-total-post-count-of-a-category-and-all-its-child-categories" title="Wordpress Codex" target="_blank"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Zb3TKe1YK-vNSHQgY3X3arbXv_0/0/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Zb3TKe1YK-vNSHQgY3X3arbXv_0/0/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a><br/>\n<a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Zb3TKe1YK-vNSHQgY3X3arbXv_0/1/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Zb3TKe1YK-vNSHQgY3X3arbXv_0/1/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a></p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:114:"http://www.snilesh.com/resources/wordpress/total-post-count-of-a-category-and-its-child-categories-wordpress/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:47:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"Add Custom Image Headers to your WordPress.org plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:98:"http://www.snilesh.com/resources/wordpress/add-custom-image-headers-to-your-wordpress-org-plugins/";s:7:"attr