n developer. WordPress.org added custom headers on wordpress plugin pages as part of an experiment, All plugin developers can now customize their plugin page with customized banner image of specified size 772&#215;250 px on top header section of their plugin page.</p>\n<p>WordPress developer can now add 772&#215;250 px JPG/PNG banner image or picture on top of their WordPress.org plugin page. To check this feature in action you can check <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/social-toolbar/" title="social toolbar" target="_blank">social toolbar</a> plugins page on wordpress.org website. </p>\n<h3>How to Add Image in WordPress Plugin Page Header</h3>\n<p>1] Create one 772×250 px sized PNG or a JPG / JPEG image or banner for your wordpress plugin. GIF images are not supported for this image.</p>\n<p>2] If you are using windows os then create one directory named &#8216;assets&#8217; inside your plugins root location at the same level where your trunk directory located and not inside trunk directory.<br />\n<img src="http://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/assets.jpg" alt="Assets" title="assets" width="437" height="155" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1623" /></p>\n<p>3] Now rename your banner / picture / Image which you created in first step, rename it to banner-772&#215;250.[jpeg/jpg/png]. And Save that inside &#8220;<strong>assets</strong>&#8221; directory which you created in second step.</p>\n<p>4] Now right click on assets folder and select TortoiseSVN->Add. This will add both the assets directory and the banner image to your code in the SVN.</p>\n<p>5] Wait for 15 minutes to get plugin pages get updated. </p>\n<p>Credits<br />\n<a href="http://wpdevel.wordpress.com/2011/12/21/been-giving-a-lot-of-thought-to-how/" title="WP Dev" target="_blank"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/14Dso7Dzw40-SzFMghmv5E5z7gU/0/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/14Dso7Dzw40-SzFMghmv5E5z7gU/0/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a><br/>\n<a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/14Dso7Dzw40-SzFMghmv5E5z7gU/1/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/14Dso7Dzw40-SzFMghmv5E5z7gU/1/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a></p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:103:"http://www.snilesh.com/resources/wordpress/add-custom-image-headers-to-your-wordpress-org-plugins/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:80:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"wordpress rating plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://www.snilesh.com/resources/wordpress/wordpress-rating-plugins/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:77:"http://www.snilesh.com/resources/wordpress/wordpress-rating-plugins/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 28 Dec 2011 13:14:37 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:14:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Wordpress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s: