/blog theme packed with (custom) features, a filterable portfolio, a bunch of custom widgets, a couple of custom page templates, a boat load of awesomeness and much more:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="wpthemes_image_preview"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/skramble/full_screen_preview/2372668?ref=neel" title="Download "Skramble" target="_blank"><img src="http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/01_preview.__large_preview21.jpg&a=t&w=500"a lt="Skramble" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Adaptive design</strong> – tired of zooming in and out when viewing your website on a mobile device? Skramble is built to be ‘adaptive’ wich means that it adapts to the device being used! No more zooming with layouts that adapt to desktop, tablet (tested on iPad) and mobile (tested on iPhone).</p>\n<p><strong>Custom portfolio posttype</strong> – want to show of your creativity? Do so in a creative and attractive way with the built in custom portfolio posttype! On the front-end you can filter portfolio items by using the filter displayed on top of the portfolio page. On the back-end portfolios can be sorted with a simple drag-n-drop system!</p>\n<p><strong>Post formats</strong> – like to blog much? Display your blogs in a visually stunning way. All the usual post-format suspects are supported and styled in a unique way. every post-format has it’s own look and feel to it. That way your visitors know in an instant what kind of blog-post they are dealing with!</p>\n<p><strong>Styles drop-down menu</strong> – out with shortcodes and in with the styles drop-down menu! See directly how your posts get styled in the Tiny MCE Editor. No more messing around with complicated shortcodes and all the madness that comes a long with it. The styles drop-down menu supports: buttons, toggles, pull-quotes, alerts, columns, v- and x-lists and text-highlighting.</p>\n<h2>What you’re getting when you purchase Skramble:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Awesome jQuery isotope grid based layout</li>\n<li>Adaptive design</li>\n<li>Custom theme options (customize Skramble to your liking by the click of a mouse, yes it’s that easy!)</li>\n<li>Custom portfolio posttype (show off your creativity)</li>\n<li>Filterable portfolio (on the front-end)</li>\n<li>Drag-n-drop sortable portfolio (on the back-end)</li>\n<li>Post format support (standard, aside, link, quote, status, image, gallery, audio, video and chat)</li>\n<li>Fixed or relative top-bar (tagline &amp; navigation)</li>\n<li>Sticky sidebar (Enable/disable it, whatever you like)</li>\n<li>Full localisation support (.po/.mo files are included, as is the dutch translation)</li>\n<li>Bunch of custom page templates (archives, contact, portfolio, homepage and full-width)</li>\n<li>Layered PSD files (for customisation purposes)</li>\n<li>Well documented (so you won’t miss a thing)</li>\n<li>WordPress 3.1+ ready (menu’s, featured images and post-formats)</li>\n<li>Now with custom backgrounds (since v1.1)</li>\n<li>And a lot more!</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:50:"http://wordpressskins.org/1728/skramble.html/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:83:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27:"Folio Two WordPress Edition";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s: