ot be a problem to show your favorite works.</p>\n<p>If you are a DRIBBBLE player/fan you can show your latest shots in a original and easy way.</p>\n<p>Just select your best works and begins to show your talent!</p>\n<div class="wpthemes_image_preview"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/folio-two-wordpress-edition/full_screen_preview/2351272?ref=neel" title="Download "Folio Two WordPress Edition" target="_blank"><img src="http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/00-preview.jpg&a=t&w=500"a lt="Folio Two WordPress Edition" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dribbble integration</li>\n<li>Cool filtering method</li>\n<li>Custom galleries for showing your works</li>\n<li>Custom backgrounds for your galleries</li>\n<li>Custom lightbox system based on PrettyPhoto</li>\n<li>Google fonts. More than 75 fonts available.</li>\n<li>Ajax template</li>\n<li>HTML5 history</li>\n<li>Three different navigations. Left sided (fixed &amp; sliding) and a top navigation, you can choose between them in a very easy way.</li>\n<li>Lightbox showcase mode</li>\n<li>Two different galleries. The classic gallery based in Folio Two HTML5 and a new one. You can see the new one in the live preview</li>\n<li>Vimeo &amp; Youtube video support</li>\n<li>Change the thumbs size directly from the option panel</li>\n<li>You can adjust the transparency for the thumbs using a simple slider within the panel too</li>\n<li>Adjust the sizes for your text, fonts, color. Combinations are unlimited.</li>\n<li>Lightbox showcase mode</li>\n<li>Semantic HTML5 structure &amp; Degrades Gracefully</li>\n<li>iOS/Mobile Ready</li>\n<li>iOS gestures and keyboard support for galleries</li>\n<li>A very easy to use control panel where you could change your logos, adjust positions, change fonts, colors and customize your portfolio in a very easy way.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>UPDATES :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>3 JUN : Version 1.11</strong><br />\n· Improved the use of videos from Youtube/Vimeo. Now you can modify the width as you need.<br />\n· Added shortcodes to improve the content addition to default pages and fixed the ratio problem with responsive behaviors in these pages.<br />\n· Added the option to change the background color for the main grid<br />\n· Preloader simplified with the option to use an advanced one.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>28 MAY : Version 1.1</strong><br />\n· Fixed option issues. Now all the elements changed in the option panel are stored correctly</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>27 MAY Folio Two is released</strong></li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://wordpressskins.org/1732/draft-created-june-20-2012-1156.html/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:86:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:36:"Bloom – Responsive WordPress Theme";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://wordpressskins.org/1723/bloom-responsive-wordpress-theme.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:77:"http://wordpressskins.org/1723/bloom-responsive-wordpress-theme.html#comm