etized Footer</li>\n<li>WordPress Custom Menu Support</li>\n<li>Unlimited Sidebars. Create and select any sidebar for each page.</li>\n<li>Portfolio 1,2,3,4 Columns</li>\n<li>100+ Google &amp; Custom Cufon Fonts.</li>\n<li>Light / Dark Skin</li>\n<li>Unlimited Color Skinning Options</li>\n<li>6 Custom Widgets</li>\n<li>Twitter / Flickr / Popular Posts / Recent Posts / Contact Info/ Contact Form / Text Widget Support Shortcodes.</li>\n<li>90+ Custom Shortcodes</li>\n<li>Sidebar Footer</li>\n<li><strong>WordPress MU Compatible</strong></li>\n<li>OOP Framework.</li>\n<li>Custom Post Type</li>\n<li>Portfolio</li>\n<li>Portfolio Single Page with Attachment sliders</li>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Built in Shortcode Generator.</li>\n<li>Advanced Options Panel (Import or Export the theme options panel settings.)</li>\n<li>Google Map Integrated</li>\n<li>Blog Style Layouts shortcode</li>\n<li>Blog single post and threaded comments</li>\n<li>This theme skinning options empowers you to change any elements such as backgrounds, texts, links, menu, typography, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Localization</h2>\n<p>This theme is Internationalization and localization built into its structure to easily used for different languages. POT File will be included soon in 1.1 version</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://wordpressskins.org/1702/coreden-responsive-wordpress-theme.html/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:77:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base